---
// Shared site footer. Tool pages render their how-it-works + FAQ above this in
// ToolAboutCard / ToolFaqCard, so the footer itself is just the credit line.
---
<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-background)] p-6 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1080px] flex-col items-center gap-2">
    <p class="m-0 text-[0.85rem] text-[var(--color-muted)]">
      Built with ❤️ by <a class="font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/shlomsh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shlomi Shemesh</a>.
      <span class="ml-2 inline-flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-[0.4rem] gap-y-[0.3rem]">
        <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-[0.3rem] align-middle font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/shlomsh/pdkef" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg class="shrink-0" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.58 2 12.25c0 4.53 2.87 8.37 6.85 9.73.5.1.68-.22.68-.49 0-.24-.01-.88-.01-1.72-2.79.62-3.38-1.37-3.38-1.37-.46-1.19-1.11-1.5-1.11-1.5-.91-.64.07-.62.07-.62 1 .07 1.53 1.06 1.53 1.06.89 1.56 2.34 1.11 2.91.85.09-.66.35-1.11.63-1.36-2.22-.26-4.56-1.14-4.56-5.07 0-1.12.39-2.03 1.03-2.75-.1-.26-.45-1.3.1-2.71 0 0 .84-.28 2.75 1.05a9.34 9.34 0 0 1 5 0c1.91-1.33 2.75-1.05 2.75-1.05.55 1.41.2 2.45.1 2.71.64.72 1.03 1.63 1.03 2.75 0 3.94-2.34 4.81-4.57 5.06.36.32.68.94.68 1.9 0 1.37-.01 2.47-.01 2.81 0 .27.18.6.69.49A10.02 10.02 0 0 0 22 12.25C22 6.58 17.52 2 12 2z" />
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a> &bull;
        <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-[0.3rem] align-middle font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/shlomsh/pdkef/issues/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg class="shrink-0" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M8 2l1.5 1.5" /><path d="M16 2l-1.5 1.5" /><path d="M9 6.5a3 3 0 0 1 6 0" /><path d="M6 9a6 6 0 0 0 12 0" /><path d="M12 9v11" /><path d="M20 8a3 3 0 0 1-3 3" /><path d="M4 8a3 3 0 0 0 3 3" /><path d="M21 15h-3.5" /><path d="M3 15h3.5" /><path d="M20 20a3 3 0 0 0-3-3" /><path d="M4 20a3 3 0 0 1 3-3" />
          </svg>
          Report a bug
        </a> &bull;
        <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-[0.3rem] align-middle font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/shlomsh/pdkef/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg class="shrink-0" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5C17.5 10.6 18 9.4 18 8a6 6 0 0 0-12 0c0 1.4.5 2.6 1.5 3.5.8.8 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5" /><path d="M9 18h6" /><path d="M10 22h4" />
          </svg>
          Feedback &amp; ideas
        </a> &bull;
        <a class="font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline align-middle" href="/licenses">Licenses</a>
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
